    "body": "This makes it impossible to add data to session in said callbacks. For example, the following code does not work, because session is never stored:\n\n``` python\n@app.before_request\ndef before_request():\n    u = session.get('user')\n    g.user = u and db.User(u) or None\n\n@app.after_request\ndef after_request(response):\n    session['user'] = g.user and dict(g.user) or None\n    return response\n```\n"
